<section class="section" id="work">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="kicker reveal"><span class="num">02</span><span class="lbl">What I do</span><span class="rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2 reveal"><span class="g-cyan">Three things</span><br />I spend my days on</h2>
    <div class="cards">
      <article class="card reveal d1" style="--accent: var(--pink);">
        <svg class="emblem" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <polyline points="8,34 18,24 26,30 40,13"></polyline>
          <line x1="8" y1="40" x2="41" y2="40"></line>
          <circle cx="40" cy="13" r="2.6"></circle>
        </svg>
        <h3>FinTech that respects you</h3>
        <p>Building mobile banking at Tomorrow — financial tools that are genuinely pleasant to use, without ever cutting corners on security or compliance.</p>
        <div class="meta"><span>Banking</span><span>Mobile</span><span>Compliance</span></div>
      </article>
      <article class="card reveal d2" style="--accent: var(--cyan);">
        <svg class="emblem" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="24" cy="15" r="6"></circle>
          <circle cx="11" cy="22" r="4.6"></circle>
          <circle cx="37" cy="22" r="4.6"></circle>
          <path d="M14 38c0-6 4.5-10 10-10s10 4 10 10"></path>
        </svg>
        <h3>Leading the team</h3>
        <p>Growing engineers I'd happily work for one day. Honest feedback, real code reviews, and room to make the kind of mistakes you can recover from.</p>
        <div class="meta"><span>Mentoring</span><span>Hiring</span><span>Strategy</span></div>
      </article>
      <article class="card reveal d3" style="--accent: var(--purple);">
        <svg class="emblem" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <polyline points="18,15 8,24 18,33"></polyline>
          <polyline points="30,15 40,24 30,33"></polyline>
          <line x1="27" y1="11" x2="21" y2="37"></line>
        </svg>
        <h3>Software craft</h3>
        <p>A pragmatic believer in tests and clean code. Not dogmatic about it — but a good test suite has saved me from myself more times than I can count.</p>
        <div class="meta"><span>TDD</span><span>Architecture</span><span>Quality</span></div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
